text:
Me in math today: "Time to solve some problems"

Students"How many?"
Me"As many as you need."
Students:"What?"
Me:"When you understand stop."
Students:" ............."
Me:"If I ask you why you gave an answer and you can convince me then I'm happy"
#QualityOverQuantity #iteachmath
